dvbcut (0.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New version 0.7.0
     * Add translations (from dvbcut-qt4)
     * Switched to Qt5.
     * Fix export with lavf muxer.
     * Prepare for new ffmpeg version.
  * Switch upstream repo from Sourceforge to Github.
